1
00:00:58,640 --> 00:01:00,280
Brother Hai, this is for you.

2
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:04,040
Not bad. You're sensible.

3
00:01:08,239 --> 00:01:08,840
Brother Hai.

4
00:01:10,879 --> 00:01:11,319
Alright.

5
00:01:11,799 --> 00:01:12,239
Let's go.

6
00:01:17,079 --> 00:01:18,239
Bring more next time.

7
00:01:18,719 --> 00:01:19,840
Sure, sure.

8
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:29,959
Ah Hai, I just saw your brother.

9
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:30,640
What happened to him?

10
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,879
He was... by that troublemaker A Zhan from their class...

11
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:33,959
...dragged into the third-floor restroom.

12
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:45,000
I heard you like my girlfriend.

13
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,200
No, no.

14
00:01:47,239 --> 00:01:49,200
All bark and no bite.

15
00:01:55,319 --> 00:01:56,280
Let me tell you something.

16
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:59,359
There's no one who dares to touch my girlfriend these days.

17
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:02,159
If I don't teach you a lesson today...

18
00:02:02,719 --> 00:02:05,560
...everyone will think they can mess with my people.

19
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:06,599
Stop it!

20
00:02:10,879 --> 00:02:12,439
Zhao Qihai.

21
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:18,759
You'd better stay out of this.

22
00:02:19,599 --> 00:02:20,680
He's my brother.

23
00:02:21,719 --> 00:02:23,360
If you dare touch him one more time...

24
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,599
I will definitely kill you.

25
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:31,800
The lowerclassmen are so tough these days.

26
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:34,199
Then I'd like to see...

27
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:38,280
...who kills whom today.

28
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,680
A Zhan, the principal is here!

29
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:52,719
This place is too small.

30
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:55,400
Why don't you set the time?

31
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,919
I'll set the location.

32
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,879
Anytime.

33
00:03:13,479 --> 00:03:13,960
Brother.

34
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:15,159
Are you okay?

35
00:03:16,319 --> 00:03:16,759
Get up.

36
00:03:25,039 --> 00:03:26,520
It's okay now, brother. It's okay.

37
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,639
I'm fine. Don't fight anymore.

38
00:03:29,439 --> 00:03:31,879
Brother, they're walking all over us.

39
00:03:32,639 --> 00:03:33,400
How can we let him get away with it?

40
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:37,120
It's all my fault.

41
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:41,719
You shouldn't have such a useless brother.

42
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,599
No, brother.

43
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:46,879
Brother!

44
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,120
Where are you going?

45
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,400
None of your business.

46
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,599
Ah Hai! Ah Hai!

47
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:01,919
Bad news!

48
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:03,360
Your brother was dragged away by A Zhan and his gang again!

49
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,280
I'm not getting involved in his business anymore.

50
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:10,479
What? He's your brother, after all.

51
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:11,800
If he gets beaten, you'll lose face.

52
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,319
He told me not to get involved.

53
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:17,160
But what if someone gets killed?

54
00:04:20,199 --> 00:04:20,759
Ah Hai!

55
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,040
Ah Hai, say something!

56
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:22,399
Ah Hai!

57
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:28,199
You're pathetic. I'm hitting you...

58
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,319
...and you're still smiling?

59
00:04:29,879 --> 00:04:30,319
Come here.

60
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,319
Smile.

61
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,800
Smile!

62
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:35,120
Yes, yes, yes, that's the expression.

63
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,319
Where's the money?

64
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:47,519
Thanks to Zhao Qishan for treating everyone to popsicles.

65
00:04:53,959 --> 00:04:55,279
Truly pathetic.

66
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:56,879
A Zhan, you really have a death wish.

67
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,879
Who would have thought the famous Zhao Qishan

68
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,360
was such a coward when he was young.

69
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,600
My brother isn't a coward.

70
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,360
Fine.

71
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:14,920
Go on.

72
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,319
Later,

73
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:22,920
I was expelled.

74
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,160
Where is my brother?

75
00:05:26,959 --> 00:05:29,720
Now your brother isn't at school,

76
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:31,319
no one can help you, right?

77
00:05:32,519 --> 00:05:33,319
Get him!

78
00:05:38,079 --> 00:05:39,360
How dare you bully my brother!

79
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:43,879
Someone's dead! Someone's dead! Someone's dead!

80
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,160
Get up.

81
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:48,759
Stop playing dead.

82
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:59,399
Brother, he's not breathing.

83
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:06,879
Brother.

84
00:06:08,519 --> 00:06:09,199
What are you doing?

85
00:06:09,199 --> 00:06:09,720
Brother.

86
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,920
A-Hai, remember.

87
00:06:12,199 --> 00:06:13,319
He was still breathing just now.

88
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,639
I was the one who smashed him to death.

89
00:06:14,639 --> 00:06:16,519
Brother, what are you saying?

90
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:19,040
A Zhan bullying me is between him and me.

91
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,120
It has nothing to do with you.

92
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:22,480
Remember, no matter who asks,

93
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,240
say he was still breathing just now,

94
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,519
and I was the one who smashed him to death.

95
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,519
If I'm gone,

96
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,360
you'll be the family's only hope.

97
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,279
Don't fight anymore.

98
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:39,120
Later we realized how stupid we were.

99
00:06:40,519 --> 00:06:43,319
That blow just knocked A Zhan out.

100
00:06:44,319 --> 00:06:45,720
Because we were too nervous,

101
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:47,199
and couldn't feel his breath,

102
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,120
we thought he was dead.

103
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,639
What happened after that?

104
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:54,279
A Zhan was rushed to the hospital

105
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,560
and woke up.

106
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:58,480
My brother went to a juvenile detention center.

107
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:03,279
I became a loafer with nothing to do all day.

108
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,360
Look at me now,

109
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:09,720
living the high life every day.

110
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:13,560
I guess I haven't let down my brother's

111
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:15,199
good intentions back then.

112
00:07:18,279 --> 00:07:19,879
That's the Zhao Qishan I know.

113
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:20,759
Lies.

114
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:25,560
Mr. Zhao.

115
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:28,680
Mr. Zhao, you haven't rested yet?

116
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,759
Is he crazy?

117
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,279
I'm fine.

118
00:07:32,759 --> 00:07:34,199
I just took my medicine.

119
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:36,000
Good.

120
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,720
I told them.

121
00:07:38,199 --> 00:07:40,360
Mr. Zhao said, you,

122
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,959
you, and you,

123
00:07:43,319 --> 00:07:44,720
you are all lying.

124
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,319
Mr. Zhao.

125
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,800
Mr. Zhao, please don't be angry.

126
00:07:49,959 --> 00:07:50,959
Mr. Zhao, please don't be angry.

127
00:07:50,959 --> 00:07:51,720
I told them.

128
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,480
Everyone, don't be nervous.

129
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,480
I've already told them.

130
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,879
The circuit system is broken.

131
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,199
It's being handled.

132
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:57,360
Please don't be angry.

133
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,600
Tell me if you have any other requests.

134
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,680
Auntie Ma Shan.

135
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,720
I won't go back.

136
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,160
Let me help you to your room to rest.

137
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,680
A-Hai's story is finished.

138
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:12,920
Miss Li.

139
00:08:14,319 --> 00:08:15,519
Who goes first, you or me?

140
00:08:18,519 --> 00:08:19,519
I'm all ears.

141
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,199
Alright.

142
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:22,920
Then I'll speak first.

143
00:08:24,639 --> 00:08:25,639
A-Hai was right.

144
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:27,839
His brother, Zhao Qishan,

145
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,160
in my eyes, was simply...

146
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,159
A towering figure.

147
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:37,159
Mr. Tan.

148
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:38,840
Taicheng...

149
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,559
The crime rate has been high these past few years.

150
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,399
It's very unsafe.

151
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:43,080
This charity gala,

152
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,879
do you really have to go?

153
00:08:57,519 --> 00:08:58,159
Mr. Tan.

154
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:00,960
There is a letter for you.

155
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:02,639
Okay.

156
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:18,200
I'd actually like to see for myself

157
00:09:19,399 --> 00:09:20,480
Check its source

158
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:23,480
Mr. Tan

159
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:26,320
Mr. Tan, we'd better be careful

160
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:29,480
I've always believed Heaven protects the good

161
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:31,840
Have you found the source of the letter?

162
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:33,360
Still checking

163
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:36,480
Mr. Tan

164
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:40,600
What's going on?

165
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:46,840
Don't run!

166
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,279
Don't run! Go on, run!

167
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:51,840
Keep running!

168
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,720
Run! Run!

169
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,480
Keep running!

170
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,559
Stop!

171
00:10:03,039 --> 00:10:03,960
Who are you?

172
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:05,600
Mind your own business

173
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,320
Boss Shan, sorry about that

174
00:10:11,039 --> 00:10:11,519
Get lost

175
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,120
Young Master Tan

176
00:10:18,399 --> 00:10:20,080
I was planning to ask someone to arrange a meeting

177
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:21,720
Didn't expect to run into you here

178
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:22,960
You know me?

179
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,759
Of course

180
00:10:24,159 --> 00:10:25,879
The second son of Hancheng's Chaotian Group

181
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,159
Tan Tian, am I right?

182
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:30,159
Nice to meet you. Zhao Qishan

183
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,360
Thank you for saving me, Mr. Zhao

184
00:10:34,159 --> 00:10:34,799
Don't mention it

185
00:10:35,639 --> 00:10:37,000
Where are you heading, Mr. Tan?

186
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,039
I can give you a lift

187
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:41,120
Taicheng Trade Charity Gala

188
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,120
Mr. Zhao

189
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,879
Since you've already brought me here

190
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:50,159
why not come in and join the party with me?

191
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,200
Is that appropriate?

192
00:10:52,919 --> 00:10:53,320
Of course

193
00:10:53,919 --> 00:10:54,559
You're my friend

194
00:10:55,039 --> 00:10:55,320
After you

195
00:10:55,919 --> 00:10:56,240
After you

196
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:07,159
Mr. Tan

197
00:11:07,159 --> 00:11:09,080
This is Sheng Wen, President of the Taicheng Chamber of Commerce

198
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:10,080
Mr. Tan

199
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,399
Welcome, welcome

200
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:13,720
You're even more impressive in person

201
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,799
You're too kind, President

202
00:11:17,679 --> 00:11:18,360
This time

203
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,720
I must give you a proper tour

204
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:21,840
of our Taicheng business scene

205
00:11:22,399 --> 00:11:23,320
Let me interrupt for a moment

206
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,519
This is my friend

207
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,279
His name is Zhao Qishan

208
00:11:27,679 --> 00:11:29,919
President Sheng doesn't seem very happy to see me

209
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,200
Not at all, not at all

210
00:11:31,559 --> 00:11:34,240
I just didn't expect Mr. Tan to be your close friend

211
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,919
Both of you gracing us with your presence

212
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:37,600
welcome, welcome

213
00:11:43,879 --> 00:11:44,480
This way, please

214
00:11:44,759 --> 00:11:45,240
Sure

215
00:11:45,799 --> 00:11:46,279
Come

216
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,679
President Zhao's project

217
00:11:49,679 --> 00:11:51,360
actually has a very good direction

218
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,120
If I may be frank

219
00:11:53,519 --> 00:11:55,480
how do you know Zhao Qishan?

220
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,679
He just saved my life

221
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,039
But

222
00:12:00,039 --> 00:12:00,519
President

223
00:12:00,759 --> 00:12:01,360
Excuse me

224
00:12:01,559 --> 00:12:02,600
I need to use the restroom

225
00:12:40,559 --> 00:12:42,720
Mr. Tan, you're a man of status.

226
00:12:42,919 --> 00:12:45,200
Five million for your life isn't too much to ask, is it?

227
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,480
If you want my life, take it.

228
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:53,759
My family will burn the money for me.

229
00:12:54,679 --> 00:12:56,559
Don't dream of getting a single cent from me.

230
00:12:59,639 --> 00:13:00,320
Mr. Tan.

231
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:01,759
You really are tough.

232
00:13:02,639 --> 00:13:03,320
That's fine.

233
00:13:04,159 --> 00:13:06,399
I think someone else will agree for you.

234
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:08,320
Go ahead.

235
00:13:09,159 --> 00:13:10,120
Connect his family.

236
00:13:10,679 --> 00:13:11,639
Get his precious son.

237
00:13:11,639 --> 00:13:13,120
Let him hear his last words.

238
00:13:14,039 --> 00:13:14,360
Honey.

239
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,879
Honey, don't believe them!

240
00:13:15,879 --> 00:13:17,000
Don't give them any money, honey!

241
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:17,759
Daddy.

242
00:13:17,759 --> 00:13:18,480
Mr. Tan.

243
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:19,919
Can you hear me?

244
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:20,919
Mr. Tan.

245
00:13:22,279 --> 00:13:23,039
It's good that you're still alive.

246
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:23,720
Zhao Qishan.

247
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:26,320
I'm glad you know who I am.

248
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,399
I happen to know who you are, too.

249
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,080
Come on.

250
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:30,919
Say a word to your wife, too.

251
00:13:30,919 --> 00:13:32,320
Honey! Honey!

252
00:13:32,799 --> 00:13:33,720
Who is Mr. Zhao?

253
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,159
Is he a friend of yours?

254
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:38,759
Daddy, I'm scared.

255
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:39,559
Zhao Qishan!

256
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,480
Don't... don't do anything rash!

257
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,639
In one hour.

258
00:13:42,639 --> 00:13:45,720
Bring Mr. Tan safely to the pier warehouse.

259
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:48,840
And take your wife and child home.
